		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3fa720db e-con-full width-440 e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="3fa720db" data-element_type="container" data-settings="{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;full&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-20a8fbe1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="20a8fbe1" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
			<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Mohammed Bin Rashid City (MBR City)</h2>		</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-638d73fb text-wrap property-content elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="638d73fb" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							Mohammed Bin Rashid City (MBR City) is a creative urban development that unites elegant living and sustainability. As a renowned location in the heart of Dubai, MBR City provides world-class amenities such as some of the very best schools, healthcare institutions, and exciting retail and dining options to choose from. Riverton House community will enjoy direct access to a variety of leisure activities, including parks, sports facilities, and museums, all within minutes of their front door.
<br><br>
MBR City, located near significant attractions such as Downtown Dubai, the Ras Al Khor Wildlife Sanctuary, and the Museum of the Future, offers convenience, elegance, and an elevated standard of living. The neighbourhood provides a unique blend of active metropolitan places and serene nature retreats, creating an excellent choice for professionals, families, and investors alike. With easy access to major transit routes and the Dubai Metro, the neighbourhood connects its inhabitants to everything that Dubai has to offer, making our high-end apartments in MBR City an excellent option for anyone looking for a prime location in the hub of Dubai.						</div>
				</div>
				</div>
		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-63dc1761 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="63dc1761" data-element_type="container" data-settings="{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;full&quot;}">
